36:44.708 --> 36:46.000
Dia terpaksa pergi
ke bilik air.

36:46.166 --> 36:47.833
Saya cuba
membantu cadar awak.

36:48.000 --> 36:50.125
Wah, terima kasih banyak, Tag.

36:50.291 --> 36:52.916
